::KitKat::

She got the transmission. She was getting annouyed with these 
interuptions all the time. She looked at Megatron and 
Aracnia. "Forgive me, I must leave for a moment. I shall be right 
back."
She looked at Destructor, "Please stay here and see that our guests 
are comfortable."


She ran down the hall.  She got to the entrance and looked at the 
four bots. " DARKMOUSE! GOLDENEYE! Stand down now!"

DarkMouse::
She looked at KitKat and walked back. She stood next to KitKat, 
glaring at Koj. 

GoldenEye::
She looked at Inu and smiled. She kind of liked being called a lady.
She walked over and stood on the other side of KitKat.

KitKat::
She looked at the two bot."Hello, I am KitKat, leader of the Predacon 
and High Predacon Council Member. What is your matter of business 
here gentlebots? " She stood there, with a pleasent smile on her face 
and her wolf tail, waving slightly behind her.
